u$ are positive constants. Among others, we prove there are $\chi^*>0$ and $\{\chi_k^*\}\subset [\chi^*,\infty)$ ($\chi^*\in\{\chi_k^*\}$) such that the constant solution $( rac{a}{b}, rac{
